  EKS -->|contains| NSRTDL
  NSRTDL -->|binds identity| SARTDL
  NSRTDL -->|binds identity| SADEC
  NSRTDL -->|runs| CSFB
  NSRTDL -->|runs| IEG
  NSRTDL -->|runs| OFP
  NSRTDL -->|runs| DL
  NSRTDL -->|runs| DF
  NSRTDL -->|runs| AL

  TTRAFFIC -->|consumed by| CSFB
  TCTXE -->|consumed by| CSFB
  TCTXT -->|consumed by| CSFB
  TFLOW -->|consumed by| CSFB
  ALLOWED -->|constrains runtime semantic inputs for| CSFB

  CSFB -->|hands projection inputs to| IEG
  CSFB -->|projects joined context to| OFP
  IEG -->|supplies projection state to| OFP
  IEG -->|writes graph / entity state to| AURORA
  OFP -->|writes online feature state to| AURORA
  OFP -. reads handle from .-> REDISH

  CSFB -->|supplies context basis to| DL
  IEG -->|supplies projection basis to| DL
  OFP -->|supplies feature basis to| DL
  DL -->|hands adjudication input to| DF
  REGACTIVE -. runtime-consumed authority .-> DF
  DF -->|publishes decisions to| TRTDL
  DF -->|publishes decision audit to| TAUDIT
  AL -->|publishes action outcomes to| TAUDIT

  IEG -. retained parity relation only .-> MSF
  OFP -. retained parity relation only .-> MSF
